description:
Good morning and welcome to the ride! He is the ONE and only and you do know that. The CLO encourages a divorced woman to take a couple steps back as she begins dating after divorce. President Paquiao got a real good ring to it and Steve called it. Could the guy from Amistad and Magic Mike be the new governor of TX or nah? Somebody still trying to get their 15 minutes via Kim K. The Cleveland Browns won. The End!!! The crew discuss "physical friends" and the different situations that can come with that arrangement. Today in Closing Remarks, Uncle Steve talks about the most under promoted principle of success.
